Package: stringproc
Type: Package
Title: String Processing and Longest Common Subsequence
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Zygmunt", "Zawadzki", email = "zygmunt@zstat.pl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for string processing including finding the longest
    common subsequence between two strings using efficient C++ implementation via Rcpp.
    Includes an interactive Shiny application for visualizing string comparisons
    with color-coded output highlighting differences and common sequences.
License: GPL-3
